            "value": "<p>Your instinctive agility lets you dodge out of the way of certain area effects, such as a blue dragon's lightning breath or a <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.pbT9cw6nsjpmwrVZ]{fireball}</em> spell. When you are subjected to an effect that allows you to make a dexterity saving throw to take only half damage, you instead take no damage if you succeed on the saving throw, and only half damage if you fail. This ability does not function if you are &amp;reference[Incapacitated].</p>",
